{
  "stem": "4764.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The others were somewhere else so that in case it was-- you know, the train-- if somebody came up to you and you were suspicious, wouldn't-- you wouldn't all go, you see?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they had, let's say, taken my father, he wouldn't have said that his wife and son were on board.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were all spread out over this train from different parts of the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it looked like we were sep-- traveling separately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I said, why-- why aren't we together?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we had been, through all this period of time in such a close-- that's right-- in such a close unit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I was on the train with my mother only, and the others were all over the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, well, why aren't we together?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, you've got to be very careful and do say very much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And there were lots of officials-looking men walking down, like you see train conductors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never travel on trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't like [INAUDIBLE] train conductors either, [LAUGHS] because they always looked like they were-- was asking you for-- for tickets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they said, you've got to be very careful if they come up and ask you for your name or your ticket.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know I never traveled on trains?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Isn't that strange?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yeah, so [LAUGHS] I didn't-- so we-- this had to be-- it was very-- it was very worrying, and I remember being very nervous because my mother instilled this in me, how serious the situation was.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought, well, here we are in heaven already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she said, no, we've got to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to be-- it was important not to say too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
